// Clowder & Crest todo folder — strict whitelist.
//
// Syncthing evaluates rules top-down, first match wins. Lines starting with
// '!' mean "include" (don't ignore). Everything else is an ignore pattern.
// The final catch-all '*' means: anything NOT explicitly included above is
// ignored. This prevents a repeat of the 2026-04-06 incident where a Mac
// Syncthing pointed at ~ pulled the entire home directory into this folder.
//
// If you need to add a new subdirectory or file type, ADD IT TO THIS FILE
// FIRST, then let Syncthing rescan — don't just drop files in and hope.

// Allow markdown files at the root (claude-todo.md, jacob-done.md, etc)
!/*.md
!/*.apk

// Allow the curated subdirectories that actually belong here
!/archive
!/archive/**
!/game
!/game/**
!/ideas
!/ideas/**
!/dialogue-full-screen-style-inspiration
!/dialogue-full-screen-style-inspiration/**

// Syncthing's own marker is auto-ignored by Syncthing itself, but belt-and-suspenders:
!/.stfolder
!/.stignore

// Ignore absolutely everything else at any depth
*
